Construct2D.jl
==============

Copyright (C) 2026  Antonios Gementzopoulos

This package is a pure-Julia reimplementation (translation) of Construct2D, a
structured grid generator for 2D airfoils originally written in Fortran by
Daniel Prosser:

    Construct2D
    Copyright (C) 2013-2018  Daniel Prosser
    https://sourceforge.net/projects/construct2d/

Because Construct2D.jl is a derivative work of that GPL-licensed program, it is
distributed under the same license:

